  "title": "feat(instantsearch): hydrate search client",
  "body": "This draft PR shows a proof of concept of hydrating the search client with initial results obtained during server-side rendering, so that the initial client-side request hits the cache.\r\n\r\nThe code is adapted from the implementation that worked in React InstantSearch v6: https://github.com/algolia/react-instantsearch/blob/master/packages/react-instantsearch-core/src/core/createInstantSearchManager.js#L329.\r\n\r\n**results**:\r\n\r\nfixes #5864\r\nfixes #5839\r\nFX-2647",
